title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1990-02-27
description:
Set 1

Let The Good Times Roll, Feel Like A Stranger, Sugaree, Victim Or The Crime, Mississippi Half Step, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song

Set 2

Iko Iko*, Women Are Smarter*, Standing On the Moon, Truckin'-> Spoonful-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Morning Dew-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: We Bid You Good Night

* with Michael Doucet fiddle and ?? banjo from Beausoleil
